title: Audi A4 Avant original Service & Maintenance Manual 1995-2000
description:
This is a full copy of an original service and rapair manual for the Audi A4 Avant covering 1995-2000.

Including more than 500 pdf-files and containing the following chapters:
- Body
- Electrical Equipment
- Engine Mechanical
- Fuel Injection and Ignition
- Fuel System
- Heating & AC
- Maintenance
- Suspension, Wheel & Brakes
- Transmission

Just unzip the file and start reading !
